<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>mạ ạ̉ʿjb ạlnʿmẗ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 mạ ạ̉ʿjb ạlnʿmẗ ly mn qlbk ạlkbyr
 mn bʿd mạ dẖqt ạlʿạlm hạ ạ̹nny bṣyr
 ạlnʿmẗ qd wḍʿt ṣwtk fy ạlqlb
 wạlnʿmẗ qd ḥyrt qlby mn ạlrb
 The Lord has promised good to me
 His word my hope secures
 He will my shield and portion be
 As long as life endures</lyrics>
<author>John Newton</author>
<hymn_number>6265</hymn_number>
</song>